<h2 id="install-tigertango">Step 2: Install TigerTango</h2>

<p>The simplest way to install TigerTango is directly from within Virtual DJ.</p>

<h3>Install from Virtual DJ</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Open Virtual DJ and click <strong>Settings</strong> (gear icon in upper right)</li>
  <li>Select the <strong>Interface</strong> tab (computer monitor icon)</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Get More</strong></li>
  <li>Type <strong>TigerTango</strong> in the search box</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Install</strong></li>
  <li>Return to the Interface tab</li>
  <li>Select the <strong>TigerTango</strong> skin (it should now appear as an option)</li>
